<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Order Success | BuyKaro</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
      background-color: #000;
      color: #fff;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
    }

    .container {
      background-color: #111;
      border: 1px solid #222;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 40px;
      max-width: 450px;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    }

    .checkmark {
      font-size: 60px;
      color: #00ff99;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #ccc;
      margin: 8px 0;
    }

    .order-id {
      background-color: #000;
      border: 1px solid #333;
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 6px 12px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 10px 0;
      color: #fff;
      font-family: monospace;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #fff;
      color: #000;
      border: none;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-top: 20px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .button:hover {
      background-color: #00ff99;
      color: #000;
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    @media (max-width: 500px) {
      .container {
        width: 90%;
        padding: 30px;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="checkmark">âœ”</div>
    <h1>Order Placed Successfully</h1>
    <p>Thank you, <strong><%= user.username %></strong>!</p>
    <p>Your order ID:</p>
    <div class="order-id"><%= new Date().getTime() %></div>
    <p>A confirmation email has been sent to <strong><%= user.email %></strong>.</p>
    <p>We appreciate your business and hope you enjoy your purchase!</p>
    <a href="/" class="button">Continue Shopping</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
